data.description: Welcome to this fantastic opportunity in Calumet City! Presenting a well-maintained 3-unit building available for sale in "as-is" condition. This property, located in a sought-after neighborhood, offers tremendous potential for investors and homeowners alike. With a total of three spacious units, this building provides a diverse range of possibilities. Each unit features comfortable living spaces, ample natural light, and functional layouts that maximize the use of every square foot.   This property enjoys a convenient location with easy access to a host of amenities. Residents will appreciate being in proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, restaurants, and other essential services. Commuting is a breeze, thanks to the property's close proximity to major highways and public transportation options.  As you step onto the property, you'll immediately notice its excellent curb appeal, with a charming exterior that exudes character. Aesthetically pleasing, this property will capture the attention of anyone seeking a reliable investment opportunity. Rents are currently under market value with room for increase.
